        "Fail": "\u5831\u916C\u91D1\u30BC\u30ED\r\n\u30BF\u30A4\u30E0\u30A2\u30C3\u30D7"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Rumble in the Jungle",
        "Client": "Curious Coward",
        "Description": "I\u0027ve been hearing this sound\r\nfrom the Jungle lately\u2014a kind\r\nof electric buzzing? I admit\r\nI\u0027m curious, but I get shivers\r\nthinking about what awaits at\r\nthe source. Think you could\r\ntake a look, Hunter?",
        "Target": "Hunt a Tobi-Kadachi",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Du rififi dans la Jungle",
        "Client": "Poltron curieux",
        "Description": "Depuis quelque temps, j\u0027entends\r\nun bruit bizarre dans la Jungle,\r\ncomme un bourdonnement\r\n\u00E9lectrique. J\u0027aimerais savoir\r\nce qu\u0027il en est, mais j\u0027ai peur !\r\nTu pourrais m\u0027aider ?",
        "Target": "Chasser un Tobi-Kadachi",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Che rumore fa la giungla",
        "Client": "Codardo curioso",
        "Description": "Sento un suono provenire dalla\r\ngiungla... Una specie di ronzio\r\nelettrico? Sono curioso, ma mi\r\nvengono i brividi solo a pensare\r\na cosa potrebbe aspettarmi\r\nlaggi\u00F9. Puoi dare un\u0027occhiata?",
        "Target": "Caccia un Tobi-Kadachi",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Donner im Dschungel",
        "Client": "Neugieriger Feigling",
        "Description": "Seit Kurzem h\u00F6re ich dieses\r\nGer\u00E4usch aus dem Dschungel\u2013 eine\r\nArt elektrisches Surren? Ich\r\nbin neugierig, bekomme aber\r\nG\u00E4nsehaut bei der Vorstellung, was\r\nmich erwarten mag. Kannst du\r\nf\u00FCr mich nachsehen?",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Tobi-Kadachi.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Bronca en la Jungla",
        "Client": "Cobardica curioso",
        "Description": "\u00DAltimamente llega un ruido de\r\nla Jungla, una especie de\r\n\u00BFzumbido el\u00E9ctrico? Tengo\r\ncuriosidad, pero pensar en lo\r\nque lo produce me da\r\nescalofr\u00EDos. \u00BFPodr\u00EDas ir a\r\nechar un vistazo?",
        "Target": "Caza un Tobi-Kadachi",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u0413\u0443\u043B \u0432 \u0414\u0436\u0443\u043D\u0433\u043B\u044F\u0445",
        "Client": "\u041B\u044E\u0431\u043E\u043F\u044B\u0442\u043D\u044B\u0439 \u0442\u0440\u0443\u0441",
        "Description": "\u0412 \u043F\u043E\u0441\u043B\u0435\u0434\u043D\u0435\u0435 \u0432\u0440\u0435\u043C\u044F \u0434\u043E \u043C\u0435\u043D\u044F\r\n\u0434\u043E\u043D\u043E\u0441\u0438\u0442\u0441\u044F \u043D\u0435\u043A\u0438\u0439 \u0437\u0432\u0443\u043A \u0438\u0437\r\n\u0414\u0436\u0443\u043D\u0433\u043B\u0435\u0439 \u2014 \u043A\u0430\u043A\u043E\u0435-\u0442\u043E \u0436\u0443\u0436\u0436\u0430\u043D\u0438\u0435.\r\n\u041F\u0440\u0438\u0437\u043D\u0430\u044E\u0441\u044C, \u043C\u043D\u0435 \u043B\u044E\u0431\u043E\u043F\u044B\u0442\u043D\u043E,\r\n\u043D\u043E \u043E\u0442 \u043C\u044B\u0441\u043B\u0438 \u043E\u0431 \u0438\u0441\u0442\u043E\u0447\u043D\u0438\u043A\u0435\r\n\u0437\u0432\u0443\u043A\u0430 \u043C\u0435\u043D\u044F \u0431\u0440\u043E\u0441\u0430\u0435\u0442 \u0432 \u0434\u0440\u043E\u0436\u044C.\r\n\u041F\u043E\u0441\u043C\u043E\u0442\u0440\u0438\u0448\u044C, \u0447\u0442\u043E \u0442\u0430\u043C?",
        "Target": "\u0412\u044B\u0441\u043B\u0435\u0434\u0438\u0442\u044C \u0422\u043E\u0431\u0438-\u041A\u0430\u0434\u0430\u0447\u0438",
